      "num": "02 · the move",
      "heading": "Publish the useful artifact",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">Share a debugging note, diagram, checklist, or mistake with enough context that someone else can use it. You do not need to pretend it is the final word.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "file": "learning-note.md",
          "code": "What I thought:\nWhat changed my mind:\nHow I tested it:\nWhat I still do not know:",
          "caption": "A caveat section is a power move."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "num": "03 · the check",
      "heading": "Keep a private workbench",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">Not every note needs an audience. Private scratchpads protect the messy part of learning so public sharing can stay honest.</p>"
        },
